      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To debug SAIL domain we need to connect the Lauterbach with SAIL JTAG. This page is to analyze the JTAG connection of SAIL"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Seems all the HW connection are already available in VCU PROs 8255"
    },
